You have a child and won't admit it?

00:31:22.319 --> 00:31:22.640
I didn't!

00:31:22.640 --> 00:31:24.160
Be a human being, you jerk! Get lost!

00:31:25.160 --> 00:31:25.720
Don't follow me!

00:31:46.160 --> 00:31:46.559
Guifang.

00:31:47.480 --> 00:31:47.880
Xurui.

