About this matter...

00:31:49.440 --> 00:31:50.599
I shouldn't have told you,

00:31:50.759 --> 00:31:52.079
but today you must listen to me.

00:31:52.799 --> 00:31:54.240
Kong Xiaocan is a scumbag.

00:31:54.559 --> 00:31:55.200
One word: Split.

00:31:55.519 --> 00:31:56.039
