You said it!

00:32:25.400 --> 00:32:27.359
You said you and Xiaocan have a child,

00:32:27.720 --> 00:32:28.960
and the child is quite big already.

00:32:29.000 --> 00:32:32.000
That's why Xiaocan had to earn money to support the family.

