Stop.

00:32:33.440 --> 00:32:34.200
What I meant was...

00:32:34.599 --> 00:32:35.640
there are just two people in our family.

00:32:35.880 --> 00:32:36.640
Since I'm preparing for exams,

00:32:36.759 --> 00:32:38.319
Kong Xiaocan has to focus on supporting the family.

00:32:46.200 --> 00:32:46.599
No...

00:32:47.480 --> 00:32:48.880
You got pregnant unexpectedly,

00:32:49.279 --> 00:32:51.200
so Xiaocan had to drop out of school.

00:32:51.359 --> 00:32:52.960
You didn't tell us because...

00:32:54.200 --> 00:32:55.160
I am his mom.

