I am his mom.

00:33:14.000 --> 00:33:15.160
I had a serious illness,

00:33:15.400 --> 00:33:17.319
and used an experimental drug.

00:33:17.519 --> 00:33:18.599
That's why I look like this now.

00:33:18.759 --> 00:33:20.039
I look a bit young,

00:33:24.880 --> 00:33:26.480
but I don't have a child.

00:33:26.519 --> 00:33:27.319
Really.

00:33:27.839 --> 00:33:29.640
At least give me a chance to explain!

00:33:29.720 --> 00:33:31.279
I'm an innocent guy!

00:34:10.079 --> 00:34:11.159
When is the East Lake Jump?

00:34:18.280 --> 00:34:18.760
Take a look.

00:34:23.719 --> 00:34:25.039
What are you showing me?

00:34:29.320 --> 00:34:29.760
Just look.

00:34:30.199 --> 00:34:30.840
That expression...

00:34:31.599 --> 00:34:32.199
The hand...

00:34:33.519 --> 00:34:33.960
The eyes...

00:34:40.639 --> 00:34:42.840
Although I don't know about your high school days,

00:34:43.440 --> 00:34:44.920
judging from this period of time,

00:34:45.159 --> 00:34:46.840
I think Kong Xiaocan is a jerk.

00:34:48.360 --> 00:34:50.039
But after editing just now,

00:34:52.119 --> 00:34:52.920
I feel...

00:34:54.519 --> 00:34:56.360
you still care about him.

00:34:56.639 --> 00:34:58.639
You really like him, really love him.

00:35:04.719 --> 00:35:05.400
Xurui.

