Let's eat together then.

00:35:16.519 --> 00:35:17.239
Not in the mood.

00:35:20.719 --> 00:35:22.960
These two are really worrying.

00:35:23.800 --> 00:35:25.960
Isn't that because of your good friend Kong Xiaocan?

00:35:26.519 --> 00:35:27.400
When he was good with Xurui,

00:35:27.400 --> 00:35:28.599
it felt like he'd give his life for her.

