One minute he disappears,

00:35:30.280 --> 00:35:31.360
the next he's suddenly all affectionate.

00:35:31.920 --> 00:35:32.960
I don't know what he's thinking.

00:35:33.480 --> 00:35:34.280
It's so annoying.

